<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TVM4.10.6">
<l>pōṟṟi maṟṟōr teyvam pēṇap puṟattiṭ ṭummaiyiṉṉē</l>
<l>tēṟṟi vaittatel līrum vīṭu peṟṟālula killaiyeṉṟē</l>
<l>cēṟṟil cennel kamala mōṅku tirukkuru kūrataṉu</l>
<l>ḷāṟṟa vallavaṉ māyaṅ kaṇṭīra taṟintaṟin tōṭumiṉē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>While you praise [and] honour another god there is placing you outside</l>
<l>[and] clearly putting you thus. If you all attain liberation the world is no [more]. Thinking so,</l>
<l>look at the wonders of the one able to comfort Tirukkurukūr, high</l>
<l>red paddy [and] lotuses in the mud. Knowing [and] knowing that run.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
